ServiceNow requires the completion of the following prerequisite training course(s) in
preparation for the Certified Application Developer exam.

Within the following link: https://nowlearning.service-now.com/lxp?id=overview&sys_id=2080f328db1e7300de3cdb85ca9619bf&type=path

Information provided in the following ServiceNow training course(s) contain source material for the exam:

• Scripting in ServiceNow Fundamentals.

• Automated Test Framewor.

• Application Development Fundamentals.

*Upon completion, the candidate will be issued a voucher code to register for the Certified Application Developer exam.
